        Getting started with NelliTab

        After a fresh install the local icon database is empty. NelliTab is not making extra Ajax or any other bulk requests to external servers to get missing icons automatically.

        You need to visit a website to refresh an icon or to use shift and click on a bookmark for uploading an custom image. But note not all websites provide always modern "Touch" icons.

        Shift and click offers you as well to edit bookmarks, to remove entries from the history and to add a ribbon e.g. if you do not want to mix up a public website with a local development version having same title and icon.

        Other powerfull customisations, such as changing theme, layout, wallpaper and much more, can be made in the options page of this extension.

        Please make a backup of your bookmarks first before using NelliTab!
